/wiki/Charles_Attenborough: Charles Attenborough ( 16 April 1902 - 29 August 1961 ) was a British weightlifter . He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/Weightlifting_at_the_1924_Summer_O: The men 's middleweight event was part of the weightlifting programme at the 1924 Summer Olympics . The weight class was the third-lightest contested , and allowed weightlifters of up to 75 kilograms ( 165 pounds ) . The competition was held on Wednesday , 23 July 1924 .
/wiki/John_Austin_(weightlifter): John Austin ( born 1900 , date of death unknown ) was a British weightlifter . He competed in the men 's middleweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/Alfred_Baxter_(weightlifter): Alfred Baxter ( 5 June 1898 - 8 January 1983 ) was a British weightlifter . He competed at the 1924 and 1928 Summer Olympics in the featherweight category ( under 60 kg ) and finished in 7th and 19th place , respectively .
/wiki/Weightlifting_at_the_1924_Summer_O: The men 's featherweight event was part of the weightlifting programme at the 1924 Summer Olympics . The weight class was the lightest contested , and allowed weightlifters of up to 60 kilograms ( 132 pounds ) . The competition was held on 21 July 1924 .
/wiki/Augustus_Cummins: Augustus Cummins ( born 1881 , date of death unknown ) was a British weightlifter . He competed in the men 's featherweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/Robert_Lowes_(weightlifter): Robert Lowes ( 1904 - 1968 ) was a British weightlifter . He competed in the men 's middleweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/William_Randall_(weightlifter): William Randall ( born 1888 , date of death unknown ) was a British weightlifter . He competed in the men 's lightweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/Weightlifting_at_the_1924_Summer_O: The men 's lightweight event was part of the weightlifting programme at the 1924 Summer Olympics . The weight class was the second-lightest contested , and allowed weightlifters of up to 67.5 kilograms ( 148.8 pounds ) . The competition was held on 22 July 1924 .
/wiki/Thomas_Taylor_(weightlifter): Thomas Taylor ( born 1889 , date of death unknown ) was a British weightlifter . He competed in the men 's featherweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/John_Tooley_(weightlifter): John Tooley ( born 4 July 1897 , date of death unknown ) was a British weightlifter . He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/William_Wyatt_(weightlifter): William Wyatt ( born 1893 , date of death unknown ) was a British weightlifter . He competed in the men 's lightweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics .
